## Results

{% sidenote %}We started working on these experiments in May 2025. Back to School is in August 2025, so the BTS 2025 numbers reflect ~3 months of compounding experiments alongside other platform improvements.{% /sidenote %}

- **Publish rate:** 68% → ~78% (+10pp) across generate and extract flows.
- **No-manual-edit publish rate:** 36.8% → 50.5% (BTS 2024 → BTS 2025) — the share of teachers who published generated assessments without any edits, a direct indicator of generation quality.
- **Document classifier impact:** +14pp publish rate for vocabulary lists, +1.4pp for worksheets.
- **Generate flow:** +5–6pp publish rate. **Extract flow:** +3–4pp publish rate.

